## 🎯 Objectives

- Monitor sales performance
- Analyze profitability
- Track order status
- Evaluate payment methods
- Generate business recommendations

## 📈 Key Metrics

- Total Profit: 70K
- Total Orders: 48
- Shipped Orders: 24
- Average Order Value: 3.08K
- Cancellation Rate: 12.5%

## 🔍 Key Insights

- Mountain Bikes generated the highest profit.
- Road Bikes ranked second in profitability.
- Credit Card was the most used payment method.
- BMX and Kids Bikes showed the lowest profitability.
- Cancellation rate reached 12.5%.

## 💡 Recommendations

- Reduce order cancellations.
- Focus marketing efforts on high-performing categories.
- Improve shipping processes.
- Review low-performing product categories.

